<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tamil Nadu</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Heritages of Tamil Nadu</h1>

    <a href="#sec1">Marina Beach</a><br>
    <a href="#sec2">Chennai Central</a><br><br>

    <img src="tamil.jpg" alt="Tamil Nadu Heritage" width="100%" height="450px">

    <h2>Brihadishvara Temple</h2>
    <p>
        Brihadishvara Temple, called Rajarajesvaram ("Lord of Rajaraja") by its builder,
        and known locally as Thanjai Periya Kovil ("Thanjavur Big Temple"), is located
        in Thanjavur, Tamil Nadu, India.
    </p>

    <div id="sec1">
        <h2>Marina Beach</h2>
        <img src="marina.jpg" alt="Marina Beach" width="100%" height="450px">
        <p>
            Marina Beach, or simply the Marina, is a natural urban beach in Chennai,
            Tamil Nadu. It is a prominent landmark in Chennai.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div id="sec2">
        <h2>Chennai Central</h2>
        <img src="central.jpg" alt="Chennai Central" width="100%" height="450px">
        <p>
            Chennai Central is the main railway station in the city of Chennai,
            Tamil Nadu, India.
        </p>
    </div>

</body>
